    • createAndSaveFaxJob

      public List<FaxJob> createAndSaveFaxJob(LoggedInInfo loggedInInfo, Map<String,Object> faxJobMap)
      1.) Creates the faxJob 2.) duplicates the faxJob for each recipient 3.) saves all the faxJobs to be sent. Map should contain values for: faxFilePath recipient recipientFaxNumber comments (for cover page) isCoverpage senderFaxNumber demographicNo copytoRecipients (as String[])

      The FaxJob list that is returned contains persisted FaxJob Objects

      Specified by:

Map should contain values for: faxFilePath recipient recipientFaxNumber comments (for cover page) isCoverpage senderFaxNumber demographicNo copytoRecipients (as String[]) The FaxJob returned is NEW UN-PERSISTED FaxJob Object with a single recipient
